::Masabot::

::Masabot was worried, because he was all alone, and Wolfgang had ditched 
him.  He was looking about, finally spotting Iron raptor, Nightstrike, and 
Prowl.  He was wondering what he should do, his thoughts shifting about in 
the back of his confused little head.  Now he knew he had made the right 
decision, pulling out two very strong handguns hidden behind his greaves, 
while his Jetpack turned on...::
